{"tha-ap49:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap49:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap49:0.3":"Sayanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap49:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap49:1.2":"mettacittassa tadino; ","tha-ap49:1.3":"Sayanaggam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap49:1.4":"dussabhandehi atthatam. ","tha-ap49:2.1":"Patiggahesi bhagava, ","tha-ap49:2.2":"kappiyam sayanasanam; ","tha-ap49:2.3":"Utthaya sayana tamha, ","tha-ap49:2.4":"vehasam uggami jino. ","tha-ap49:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap49:3.2":"yam sayanamadasaham; ","tha-ap49:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap49:3.4":"sayanassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap49:4.1":"Ekapannasito kappe, ","tha-ap49:4.2":"varako devasavhayo; ","tha-ap49:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap49:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap49:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap49:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap49:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap49:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sayanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap49:7.1":"Sayanadayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}